	   <tr><td colspan=2>Good in principle.&nbsp;&nbsp;Less than stellar in practice.  1) don't think that you'll now be able to chat - macros preempt the chat-window.  2) it only works when you don't miss notes / get interupted - if you do, then you've lost a whole cycle of twist.<br>Sorry to be a bummer, but thought I should add my perspective.<br><br>Philo<br>&nbsp;<br>Looking for love.....pity there's so little in humanity.</td></tr>
